{"id":"b8089a53-4f1d-4014-a143-8f0f9d81c37e","name":"IvГЎn Volkov","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">рҹ’—</span></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/N_U1Z9_GLi428uBqFAXbx.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/5JHOgnIs_sAr_oHrM_4X7.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 735px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">рҹ’ <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>в„•рқ•Ңрқ•„рқ”№рқ”јв„қ: рқ”Ҫрқ•Җрқ•Қрқ”ј</strong></span><strong>рҹ’ в„•рқ”јрқ•Һ в„қрқ”јв„Ӯв„қрқ•Ңрқ•Җрқ•Ӣ</strong>рҹ’ </h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/-FUbBaYNnxZrXIVZBNt4p.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 717px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/LGVusIf60ZuAv5oVMCtUv.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/7yqBC9PuvfBnrL_iAmcHE.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 723px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\">КңбҙҮ бҙӢЙӘКҹКҹбҙҮбҙ… КңЙӘs Т“бҙҖбҙӣКңбҙҮКҖ. бҙӣКңбҙҮ бҙҠбҙңбҙ…ЙўбҙҮ ЙўбҙҖбҙ бҙҮ КңЙӘбҙҚ бҙӣбҙЎбҙҸ бҙҸбҙҳбҙӣЙӘбҙҸЙҙs бҙҖЙҙбҙ… ЙӘЙҙsбҙӣбҙҮбҙҖбҙ… бҙҸТ“ ЙўбҙҸЙӘЙҙЙў бҙӣбҙҸ бҙҠбҙҖЙӘКҹ КңбҙҮ бҙ…бҙҮбҙ„ЙӘбҙ…бҙҮбҙ… бҙӣбҙҸ бҙҠбҙҸЙӘЙҙ бҙӣКңбҙҮ бҙҖКҖбҙҚКҸ...бҙҮбҙ бҙҮЙҙ КҖбҙҮКҹбҙңбҙ„бҙӣбҙҖЙҙбҙӣКҹКҸ~ <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">рҹҳ рҹ§Ё</span></p><h1><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/uUI0EAOEIkBproCDb46nZ.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 717px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">рҹ’–</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>вҷӮпёҸбҙҚбҙҖКҹбҙҮ бҙҳбҙҸбҙ вҷӮпёҸ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">рҹ’–</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> - (бҙҳКҖбҙҮ-бҙҚбҙҖбҙ…бҙҮ бҙ„КңбҙҖКҖбҙҖбҙ„бҙӣбҙҮКҖ Т“бҙҸКҖ бҙ„бҙҸЙҙбҙӣбҙҮxбҙӣ бҙҚбҙҸбҙӣЙӘбҙ бҙҮs)</span></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/JEuEJf54TqrrbzemupDvm.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/Yo0ZkW8AuVggAA1dyLw2m.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 710px; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cqv09xK2zvKLOERrMEqyM.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Not Dead Dove BUT:</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\"> </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(53, 219, 126);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">ЙҙбҙҸЙҙ-бҙ„бҙҸЙҙ</mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">/</mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">бҙ…бҙңКҷ-бҙ„бҙҸЙҙ</mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\"> - бҙҳбҙҸбҙЎбҙҮКҖ бҙҳКҹбҙҖКҸ - </mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">бҙ ЙӘбҙҸКҹбҙҮЙҙбҙ„бҙҮ</mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\"> - бҙҮxбҙҳКҹЙӘбҙ„ЙӘбҙӣ КҹбҙҖЙҙЙўбҙңбҙҖЙўбҙҮ - ЙўКҖбҙҸбҙҳЙӘЙҙЙў - </mark></em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 233, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">КҷКҖбҙҮбҙҖбҙӣКң бҙҳКҹбҙҖКҸ</mark></em></str